<h3>Crosswords</h3>

<p>In crosswords mode, enter a word pattern in the search box.  The word pattern includes
 letters known in the crossword and a period (<b>.</b>) or question mark (<b>?</b>) where the
 letter is not known.</p>

<p>Clicking the <b>Search</b> button will perform a dictionary search for any words which
 match the given pattern.  If any words are found, a list of words will be displayed.  Clicking
 on a word will display all of the definitions of the word.</p>
 
<p>To select a dictionary, select the Dictionary icon on the top menu.</p>

<p><b>NOTE:</b> The dictionary selection for this tab is independent from the dictionary
 selected in the other tabs.</p>
